node.text:
Chocolate Greek Yogurt Banana Bites
Recipe:
1 cup Greek yogurt
1 scoop @pescience chocolate bliss protein
1-2 bananas sliced 1 in
Optional: chocolate chips
Directions: mix protein & yogurt - coat banana slices and top with mini chocolate chips. Freeze 1-3 hours. Enjoy! 
_
Use code Sarah to save 15% @pescience - they have the besttt vegan protein 🌱🤩
